      <h2 id="overview-heading">System Overview</h2>
      <p>REMIS is a modern web-based application built to streamline property management workflows. It provides intuitive dashboards for admins, agents, and tenants to monitor rent, manage properties, respond to service requests, and generate detailed reports.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="features" aria-labelledby="features-heading">
      <h2 id="features-heading">Key Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Role-based dashboards for Admins, Agents, and Tenants</li>
        <li>Automated rent tracking and forecasting with AI</li>
        <li>M-PESA payment integration (STK Push & Callbacks)</li>
        <li>Service request submission and status updates</li>
        <li>Reports with PDF and Excel export options</li>
        <li>Audit trails for activity logging and security</li>
        <li>Multi-company support for scalable deployment</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="accessibility" aria-labelledby="accessibility-heading">
      <h2 id="accessibility-heading">Built with Accessibility in Mind</h2>
      <p>REMIS uses semantic HTML5 structure and ARIA landmarks to ensure full compatibility with screen readers and assistive technologies. The interface is navigable with keyboard shortcuts, and all user roles experience a clear content hierarchy.</p>
    </section>

